OL,6,FVideo report by ITV Granada Reports
OL,7,Fjournalist, Lucille Brobbey
OL,9,FThe mother of murdered teenager has
OL,10,Fcalled for smartphones to be made
OL,11,Favailable for under-16s without social
OL,12,Fmedia apps.
OL,14,FShe is also campaigning for searches
OL,15,Ffor inappropriate material to be
OL,16,Fflagged to parents.
OL,18,Fwere both 15 when they killed Brianna,
OL,19,F16, with a hunting knife after luring
OL,20,Fher to Linear Park, Culcheth, near ,
OL,21,Fon 11 February 2023.
