OL,6,FJenkinson had watched videos of
OL,7,Ftorture and murder online.
OL,9,FSpeaking on the BBC's Sunday With
OL,10,FLaura Kuenssberg, Esther Ghey said:
OL,11,F"We'd like a law introduced so that
OL,12,Fthere are mobile phones that are only
OL,13,Fsuitable for under-16s.
OL,15,F"So if you're over 16, you can have an
OL,16,Fadult phone, but then under the age of
OL,17,F16, you can have a children's phone,
OL,18,Fwhich will not have all of the social
OL,19,Fmedia apps that are out there now.
