OL,6,F"Also to have software that is
OL,7,Fautomatically downloaded on the
OL,8,Fparents' phone which links to the
OL,9,Fchildren's phone, that can highlight
OL,10,Fkey words.
OL,12,F"So if a child is searching the kind
OL,13,Fof words that Scarlett and Eddie were
OL,14,Fsearching, it will then flag up on the
OL,15,Fparent's phone."
OL,17,FShe said if the searches her
OL,18,Fdaughter's killers had made had been
OL,19,Fflagged, their parents would have been
OL,20,F"able to get some kind of help".
