OL,6,FMs Ghey said her transgender daughter
OL,7,Fhad accessed pro-anorexia and self-
OL,8,Fharm material online and been "very
OL,9,Fprotective" over her phone, which had
OL,10,Fcaused arguments.
OL,12,F"If she couldn't have accessed the
OL,13,Fsites, she wouldn't have suffered as
OL,14,Fmuch," she said.
OL,16,FDescribing the internet as the "Wild
OL,17,FWest", she said the focus of
OL,18,Ftechnology had been on making money
OL,19,Frather than "how we protect people or
OL,20,Fhow we can necessarily benefit
OL,21,Fsociety".
