OL,6,FSpeaking about Brianna, Ms Ghey said:
OL,7,F"She was absolutely full of life. She
OL,8,Fwas such a character, she was really,
OL,9,Freally outgoing.
OL,11,F"She just, she loved attention. She
OL,12,Floved to be on TikTok, she loved
OL,13,Fhaving all of the likes that she used
OL,14,Fto receive and she was the life and
OL,15,Fsoul of the party really.
OL,17,F"Everyone who knew Brianna and anybody
OL,18,Fwho ever met Brianna, would never
OL,19,Fforget her."
