OL,6,FMs Ghey said she is willing to meet
OL,7,Fthe mother of Jenkinson, who she
OL,8,Fdescribed as looking "completely
OL,9,Fbroken" and is enduring an "absolutely
OL,10,Fhorrific time".
OL,12,FShe said: "I also want her to know
OL,13,Fthat I don't blame her for what her
OL,14,Fchild's done."
OL,16,FMs Ghey added she feels like she
OL,17,Ffailed Brianna. She said: "I think as
OL,18,Fa parent I am all Brianna had, I was
OL,19,Fthe one who was supposed to look after
OL,20,Fher. Maybe if I had done things
OL,21,Fdifferently she would still be here."
