OL,6,FResponding to Ms Ghey's proposals,
OL,7,FEducation Secretary Gillian Keegan
OL,8,Fsaid the recently passed Online Safety
OL,9,FAct had "tools" to tackle the issues
OL,10,Fraised, including age verification
OL,11,Fchecks for inappropriate material.
OL,13,FShe said: "This is a massive piece of
OL,14,Flegislation, probably quite a leading
OL,15,Fposition that we've taken in really
OL,16,Fmaking sure that the platforms are
OL,17,Faccountable for proper age
OL,18,Fverification, for inappropriate things
OL,19,Fbeing unavailable and inappropriate
OL,20,Fthings, most importantly, not being
OL,21,Fthere.
